  "detailed_description": "<i>Portal Puzzle</i> combines the delightful simplicity of \"<strong>Sugar, Sugar</strong>\" with the ingenious mechanics of \"<strong>Portal</strong>.\" Dive into a world where <strong>creativity </strong>meets physics in a <strong>sandbox of possibilities</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/59db3f915fa8fefee7138ddc064b93c6.poster.avif?t=1715661082\" width=624 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/59db3f915fa8fefee7138ddc064b93c6.webm?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/59db3f915fa8fefee7138ddc064b93c6.mp4?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <i>Portal Puzzle</i>, players navigate a series of levels where the objective is to get sand to the flag. Using portals and a variety of tools at your disposal, manipulate the flow of the sand to achieve your goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/a104aa62b5e085808b073832d0b1981f.poster.avif?t=1715661082\" width=624 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/a104aa62b5e085808b073832d0b1981f.webm?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/a104aa62b5e085808b073832d0b1981f.mp4?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every level introduces a fresh twist, captivating your mind and inspiring imaginative solutions. <strong>Deceptively simple</strong> in its design, with every challenge offering an <strong>elegant solution</strong>, <i>Portal Puzzle</i> is an invitation to <strong>think differently.</strong><br><br>Music by Quint Hutchinson",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Portal Puzzle</i> combines the delightful simplicity of \"<strong>Sugar, Sugar</strong>\" with the ingenious mechanics of \"<strong>Portal</strong>.\" Dive into a world where <strong>creativity </strong>meets physics in a <strong>sandbox of possibilities</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/59db3f915fa8fefee7138ddc064b93c6.poster.avif?t=1715661082\" width=624 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/59db3f915fa8fefee7138ddc064b93c6.webm?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/59db3f915fa8fefee7138ddc064b93c6.mp4?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <i>Portal Puzzle</i>, players navigate a series of levels where the objective is to get sand to the flag. Using portals and a variety of tools at your disposal, manipulate the flow of the sand to achieve your goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/a104aa62b5e085808b073832d0b1981f.poster.avif?t=1715661082\" width=624 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/a104aa62b5e085808b073832d0b1981f.webm?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2611630/extras/a104aa62b5e085808b073832d0b1981f.mp4?t=1715661082\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Every level introduces a fresh twist, captivating your mind and inspiring imaginative solutions. <strong>Deceptively simple</strong> in its design, with every challenge offering an <strong>elegant solution</strong>, <i>Portal Puzzle</i> is an invitation to <strong>think differently.</strong><br><br>Music by Quint Hutchinson",
